The simplest approach: `sendQuoteAction` already works for any quote type since it just needs `clientEmail`, `clientName`, `title`, and the quote URL. Add `"ai-generated"` awareness only if the URL or behavior needs to differ. For now, just export a thin alias or let `sendQuoteAction` handle it:

